      "rationale": "Linear elastic material model justified by the predominantly elastic response regime under F1717 loading. Contact between screw and block modeled with frictional contact (mu=0.2) consistent with titanium-on-UHMWPE interface literature values. Large-displacement formulation enabled to capture geometric nonlinearity at 40 mm displacement."
