      "rationale": "Testing performed at a single load configuration per ASTM F1717 standard protocol. Only one test condition (static compression-bending at prescribed displacement rate) was employed. This factor is below the required level; however, the single condition is directly representative of the regulatory submission scenario and is accepted as a documented limitation."
