      "rationale": "E/uval computed for stiffness (0.83), yield force (1.12), and force at 40 mm (0.94). All values below 1.96 threshold. Percent differences: stiffness 3.1%, yield force 6.8%, force at 40 mm 4.2%, all within the <10% acceptance bound."
    },
