    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single below-threshold factor (Test conditions, achieved 1 vs. required 2) is accepted because the single test condition is directly representative of the regulatory submission scenario and N=11 experimental samples provide adequate statistical characterization of construct-to-construct variability. All three QoIs satisfy the pre-established E/uval < 1.96 and percent-difference < 10% acceptance bounds. The FEA modeling framework is judged credible for the stated COU.",
